gText_Samuel_Welcome::
	.string "Hello there, my name is Samuel.\n"
	.string "It truly is a pleasure to meet you!\p"
	.string "We’re just thrilled at the prospect of\n"
	.string "you joining us here in Vyraton!\p"
	.string "I’m the mayor, so I’ll be looking after\n"
	.string "you if you decide to move here.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Samuel_Castform_Unused:: @@ See strings.c
	.string "And this is one of the friendly faces\n"
	.string "you'll see around town, Castform.{PAUSE 96}\p"

gText_Samuel_MainSpeech::
	.string "Castform is only one of the many\n"
	.string "Pokémon that inhabit the world.\l"
	.string "One of the many that live alongside us.\p"
	.string "Some of us work with Pokémon.\n"
	.string "Some people even study them.\p"
	.string "And I'm sure you know, others unite with\n"
	.string "Pokémon to battle likeminded teams.\p"
	.string "That's exactly what you would be doing,\n"
	.string "as the Gym Leader of Vyraton!\p"
	.string "It could really be a wonderful way to\n"
	.string "experience the world of Pokémon!\l"
	.string "But I’m getting ahead of myself.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Samuel_TellMeAboutYou::
	.string "Tell me a bit about you.$"

gText_Samuel_BoyOrGirl::
	.string "Are you a boy?\n"
	.string "Or are you a girl?$"

gText_Samuel_ForgottenName::
	.string "I'm so sorry!\n"
	.string "I haven’t even asked for your name yet.\l"
	.string "What should I call you?$"

gText_Samuel_SoYourePlayer::
	.string "Okay, so you're {PLAYER}{KUN}?$"

gText_Samuel_JobIsYours::
	.string "Well {PLAYER}, I think you'll fit right in.\n"
	.string "The job is most certainly yours.\p"
	.string "I cannot wait for you to see Vyraton,\n"
	.string "in all of it's radiant beauty!\p"
	.string "Nor can I wait to see your first battle\n"
	.string "as our resident Gym Leader!\p"
	.string "Though if you'll excuse me, I'll be\n"
	.string "grabbing my case and heading on my way.\p"
	.string "There's been some strange activities\n"
	.string "in the surrounding area as of late,\l"
	.string "but you need not concern yourself.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Samuel_TravelSafely::
	.string "I just know having someone like you\n"
	.string "around is going to help so much!\p"
	.string "I'll look forward to your arrival and\n"
	.string "meet you on the pier when you do.\l"
	.string "Travel safely, {PLAYER}{KUN}.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Samuel_ChooseTones::
	.string "Ah… Brilliant…\n"
	.string "Tell me more…$"
